Class ReserveSpotFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • nl.rug.nc.bicycleclient.ReserveSpotFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.arch.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, android.arch.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Callbackable<java.lang.Integer>

    public class ReserveSpotFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements Callbackable<java.lang.Integer>
    This subclass of Fragment provides the user interface where the users can choose a bicycle stand and a slot number and reserve that slot if it is empty.
